---

<section class="cnFormat" data-reveal="scroll">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title section-heading cnFormat__title" data-reveal-item="1">
      Формат <span>[ навчання ]</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="section-divider" aria-hidden="true" data-reveal-item="2"></div>

    <div class="cnGrid cnGrid--format" data-reveal-item="3">
      <article class="cnCard cnCard--format">
        <div class="cnCard__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="none">
            <path d="M12 8v5l3 2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M12 21a9 9 0 100-18 9 9 0 000 18z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="cnCard__content">
          <div class="cnCard__k">Тривалість заняття</div>
          <div class="cnCard__v">60–90 хв</div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="cnCard cnCard--format">
        <div class="cnCard__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="none">
            <path d="M16 11c1.7 0 3 1.3 3 3v6H5v-6c0-1.7 1.3-3 3-3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
            <path d="M12 12a4 4 0 100-8 4 4 0 000 8z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="cnCard__content">
          <div class="cnCard__k">Формати</div>
          <div class="cnCard__v">Індивідуальні, парні, групові (3–5)</div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="cnCard cnCard--format">
        <div class="cnCard__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="none">
            <path d="M12 21s7-4.6 7-11a7 7 0 10-14 0c0 6.4 7 11 7 11z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
            <path d="M12 10.5a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="cnCard__content">
          <div class="cnCard__k">Офлайн</div>
          <div class="cnCard__v">м.Київ, метро Академмістечко</div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="cnCard cnCard--format cnCard--accentOnline">
        <div class="cnCard__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="none">
            <path d="M12 18h.01" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M8.5 15.5a5 5 0 017 0" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M6 13a8 8 0 0112 0" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="cnCard__content">
          <div class="cnCard__k">Онлайн</div>
          <div class="cnCard__v">Zoom / Google Meet / Microsoft Teams</div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="cnCard cnCard--format">
        <div class="cnCard__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="none">
            <path d="M12 3l9 5-9 5-9-5 9-5z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
            <path d="M3 13l9 5 9-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="cnCard__content">
          <div class="cnCard__k">Матеріали</div>
          <div class="cnCard__v">Доступ до Miro, Canva або Figma з усіма матеріалами з уроків</div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="cnCard cnCard--format">
        <div class="cnCard__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="none">
            <path d="M4 4h16v12H7l-3 3V4z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <path d="M8 8h8M8 12h6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="cnCard__content">
          <div class="cnCard__k">Підтримка</div>
          <div class="cnCard__v">Онлайн-словник (оновлюється після кожного уроку) + Telegram канал</div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
